We found 175 records using the search strategy, and 11 additional records by checking references of the included articles. After title and abstract screening, 44 articles were excluded because they were duplicates, and 108 papers were selected for screening by title and abstract. After the examination of exclusion criteria, a total of 47 articles were finally included (Fig. 1
). All the included articles were published in English, and all of them achieved viral RNA amplification. The assessment of the quality of the information in each article is shown in Fig. 2
.
